name: title
Gatto 5mm beam WT 36 wks: Kinematic of 36-week-old WT mice walking on a 5 mm wide beam

name: description
Gatto 5mm beam WT 36 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 36-week-old C57BL/6J mice walking on a wide 5 mm beam. Control Group. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
